      "content": "therapists and agencies wont change the fact that i owe more than i could ever make in ten lifetimes. it's not just a \"hard time,\" it's a dead end. i look at my life and i just see a cage. there is no version of the future where this goes away. it's like being buried alive and everyone is just telling me to breathe deeper while the dirt keeps falling. i just want it to be over so the stress finally stops.",
